CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773993882
OL,3,CMan 'deeply upset' after parents'
OL,4,Cgravestone is cordoned off at cemetery
OL,6,F"As the cemetery authority, we are
OL,7,Frequired to carry out regular memorial
OL,8,Fsafety inspections every 5 years.
OL,10,F"Headstones can remain in place for
OL,11,Fmany years with no issues at all but
OL,12,Fground conditions can also change over
OL,13,Ftime which can affect stability.
OL,15,F"When this happens additional works
OL,16,Fare needed to bring it back to a safe
OL,17,Fand secure condition and the
OL,18,Fregistered grave owner is responsible
OL,19,Ffor arranging and funding any remedial
OL,20,Fworks required.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773993882
OL,3,CMan 'deeply upset' after parents'
OL,4,Cgravestone is cordoned off at cemetery
OL,6,F"A permit fee of #78 is payable to
OL,7,Fallow an approved stonemason to carry
OL,8,Fout work within the cemetery, which
OL,9,Fcovers the Council's administration
OL,10,Fcosts and oversight of the work to
OL,11,Fensure it complies with safety
OL,12,Fstandards.
OL,14,F"The fee is separate from the cost of
OL,15,Fthe repair work itself.J"The timeframe
OL,16,Ffor carrying out repairs is ultimately
OL,17,Fdetermined by the grave owner in
OL,18,Fliaison with their chosen stonemason.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
